歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17b3f6cbbc971b0c1c3961dcd048dcc332a98ae2","tid":1540641,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg11-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69474056_2643687595682310_4176666699619106816_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQk0Kb8tExi83vf2AcsDDH27FiFr3HwZ_GVK33B0W9Z_D7fvlYV0ayFSPEHoZ2ypv20&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg11-1.fna&amp;oh=c9007aee77d67dd83f9d2ccb356c3b65&amp;oe=5DF84066\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg11-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69474056_2643687595682310_4176666699619106816_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQk0Kb8tExi83vf2AcsDDH27FiFr3HwZ_GVK33B0W9Z_D7fvlYV0ayFSPEHoZ2ypv20%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg11-1.fna%26oh%3Dc9007aee77d67dd83f9d2ccb356c3b65%26oe%3D5DF84066&h=4eb3bb6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af2c3db07c5f115e3ef83b3e9211d6f41017e3c3","tid":1540641,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci